  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Why it's great</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience your favorite music like never before. The game reacts in real-time to any track you play, syncing the speed of incoming obstacles to the beat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dazzling audio-reactive particles and neon lights bring your music to life.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stellar gameplay: Spin around the center to dodge abstract shapes. With varying speeds and patterns, every playthrough offers a fresh, unique challenge.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350080/extras/1540242bafc69e72db9bad958f48e610.poster.avif?t=1773917421\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350080/extras/1540242bafc69e72db9bad958f48e610.webm?t=1773917421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350080/extras/1540242bafc69e72db9bad958f48e610.mp4?t=1773917421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How do I load my music?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Select 'My Music' in the menu to mute the in-game soundtrack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Play your favorite music on your computer – the game will sync to it instantly!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How do I play multiplayer?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To add a new player, simply press any button on a connected controller.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350080/extras/0633957c39f770db2805753ca65b96dd.poster.avif?t=1773917421\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350080/extras/0633957c39f770db2805753ca65b96dd.webm?t=1773917421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350080/extras/0633957c39f770db2805753ca65b96dd.mp4?t=1773917421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Chill or compete</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play your way: Relax with infinite lives in Casual Mode or push your limits in Hardcore Mode to climb the leaderboards. The difficulty adapts to your skill level.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Buy DLC</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get the DLC to unlock 9 additional levels, enjoy co-op for up to 6 players, and show your support for the game!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Why it's great</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience your favorite music like never before. The game reacts in real-time to any track you play, syncing the speed of incoming obstacles to the beat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dazzling audio-reactive particles and neon lights bring your music to life.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stellar gameplay: Spin around the center to dodge abstract shapes. With varying speeds and patterns, every playthrough offers a fresh, unique challenge.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350080/extras/1540242bafc69e72db9bad958f48e610.poster.avif?t=1773917421\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350080/extras/1540242bafc69e72db9bad958f48e610.webm?t=1773917421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350080/extras/1540242bafc69e72db9bad958f48e610.mp4?t=1773917421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How do I load my music?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Select 'My Music' in the menu to mute the in-game soundtrack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Play your favorite music on your computer – the game will sync to it instantly!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How do I play multiplayer?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To add a new player, simply press any button on a connected controller.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350080/extras/0633957c39f770db2805753ca65b96dd.poster.avif?t=1773917421\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350080/extras/0633957c39f770db2805753ca65b96dd.webm?t=1773917421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350080/extras/0633957c39f770db2805753ca65b96dd.mp4?t=1773917421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Chill or compete</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play your way: Relax with infinite lives in Casual Mode or push your limits in Hardcore Mode to climb the leaderboards. The difficulty adapts to your skill level.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Buy DLC</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get the DLC to unlock 9 additional levels, enjoy co-op for up to 6 players, and show your support for the game!</p>",
